{"questionId":"22001965","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>The function <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>f</mi></math> is defined by&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>f</mi><mfenced><mi>x</mi></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>4</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow></mfrac></math>, where&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi><mo>∈</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">ℝ</mi><mo>,</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>≠</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn></math>.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>The graphs of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>f</mi></math> and <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math> intersect at <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>p</mi></math> and <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>q</mi></math>, where <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>p</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mi>q</mi></math>.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Find the value of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>p</mi></math> and the value of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>q</mi></math>.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p>attempt to solve <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>f</mi><mfenced><mi>x</mi></mfenced><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mfenced><mi>x</mi></mfenced></math>&nbsp;using graph or algebraically<strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em>(M1)</em></strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>p</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></math>&nbsp; AND&nbsp;&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>q</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em>A1</em></strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</